# TLC model-checker scratch (regenerated by `tlc2.TLC`)
states/
spore_TTrace_*.tla
spore_TTrace_*.bin
*.st

# Per-run germination outputs (gate records written by `cs spore run`).
# DEFENSE-IN-DEPTH ONLY since ADR-161: germination now hands every node a
# run-scoped home under `.cosmon/state/spore-runs/<germination-id>/` (already
# gitignored), so gate records no longer land here in the first place. These
# rules remain as a backstop against a stray legacy write.
# (Future gate-output dirs follow the same pattern: <gate-name-plural>/issue-*/.)
intakes/
contracts/
implementations/
greens/
rehearsals/
releases/

# Issue-specific repro INSTANCES (written when the spore is applied to a bug).
# The reusable definition keeps only repro/README.md (the convention) and the
# generic clean-room/Dockerfile — not per-issue contracts or repro images.
repro/contract-*.md
clean-room/Dockerfile.repro*
